# CityU Guides site

- Public UI must not include developer instructions (e.g. “drop files into ebooks/”). Those belong in `README.md` / `AGENTS.md`.
- Brand colors and fonts: follow `AGENTS.md` (CityU dark blue, teal, Oswald + Avenir).
- New ebooks: add file under `site/ebooks/`, optional cover under `site/ebooks/covers/`, then append to `site/catalog.json`.
